  "tcmTraditionalUsage": {
    "en": "Derived from a type of seaweed that grows around the coasts of China and Japan, it has been valued for its medicinal properties for many centuries. Traditionally used for the pain associated with hernia disorder, it also clears heat and reduces the phlegm nodules, promotes urination and reduces oedema.\n",
